rows.label: qev090104_MSG0001
rows.name: Well, hell. This place is crawlin' with nasty critters.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0002
rows.name: You ready to go? Cause school's about to be in session.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0003
rows.name: Time to teach these indigens who owns this little piece of Mira![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Yelv that you're ready to kick some butt.

rows.label: qev090104_SEL0021
rows.name: Suggest hanging back and observing your enemy.

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0005
rows.name:
Man, this is just like when he and I used to hit the field.
Good times...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0006
rows.name:
The hell kinda plan is that?
We SEE 'em when we're BEATIN' on 'em![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0007
rows.name: He'd never have given me some horseplop idea like that...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0008
rows.name: Now let's get in there and say hello to the locals![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0009
rows.name:
Looks like the debris's got some
Earth-based animal samples in it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090104_MSG0011
rows.name:
Well, freakin' great.
Let's get back to New LA and report to Eleonora.[ST:wait ]
